The '''Lebanese–Syrian Security Apparatus''' is a network of intelligence officers and security leaders in [[Syria]] and [[Lebanon]] that is believed to have been the actual ruling power behind the government during the Syrian [[Hegemony]] period that ended in 2005.{{Citation needed|date=February 2015}}

